Cotfast: Foes of the Free People
Foes of the Free Peoples found at Cotfast should be defeated in order protect those within the Wildwood.
Foes can be found at Cotfast in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should defeat foes at Cotfast.
Foes of the Free Peoples have claimed the village of Cotfast within the Wildwood. Defeating their numbers here will assist in returning safety to the Wildwood.
